<h1>Welcome to Web Tales!</h1>
<h6>(Woo-hoo!)</h6>

<p> Web Tales is a web-app were people come and post single sentences inspired by a randomized image. Tales of derring, bad, and good luck tales. Its up to you to come up with it!
</p>

<h3>List 'O Tales</h3>
<%@tales.order(created_at: :desc).each do |tale|%>
<h4><%= link_to tale.title, tale_path(tale) %></h4>
<%end%>

<h6> <%= link_to "Add a new web tale", new_tale_path %> </h6>
<%= link_to "Order by title", tales_path(order: 'title') %>
<%= link_to "Order by recently created", tales_path %>
<%= link_to "View possible images", images_tales_url %>
